OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fbut clouding over across the west
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly cloudy with rain
OL,12,Fspreading east for a time in the
OL,13,Fmorning. Drier in the afternoon with a
OL,14,Ffew showers, some brightness across
OL,15,Fthe west. Colder than of late.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry with
OL,18,Fsome sunshine on Friday, patchy rain
OL,19,Fin the evening. Mainly dry on Saturday
OL,20,Falthough a few afternoon showers.
OL,21,FBreezy with showers on Sunday.
